People ex rel. John Evans et al. v. Saginaw Circuit Judge. Submitted June 18. Dan P. Foote for the motion. E. M. Joslin against.

Order opening judgment by defamlt not reviewable.

When the Circuit Court opens a judgment hy default, for alleged errors, it is like granting a new trial, and is not open to review.

Discretion is not reviowable on mandamus. Per Ouriam.

Motion for order to show cause.

Denied June 19.
